---
<BaseLayout title="亚马逊运营资料包中心 | 阿岩跨境笔记" description="把公开课配套的 28 个亚马逊运营资料包集中整理,按 7 个专题分类:新手规则、选品、关键词、Listing、PPC、Review、AI 工具,适合公开课前预习和课后复盘。">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(ayanBreadcrumbData)}></script>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">资源中心</div>
      <h1>亚马逊运营资料包中心</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">把关键词、Listing、PPC、Review、选品和 AI 工具资料集中整理,适合公开课前预习和课后复盘。</p>
      <div class="hero-cover">
        <img src="/images/resources/resources-center/cover.svg" alt="亚马逊卖家资源中心封面图" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-num">{resourceCategories.length}</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-label">个专题分类</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-num">{totalResources}</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-label">个资料包</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-num">28</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-label">个专题分类</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-survey-hint">
        <p>不知道先用哪份资料？做 30 秒资料诊断。</p>
        <a class="hero-survey-cta" href="/survey/">做资料诊断 →</a>
      </div>
      <a class="hero-cta" href="#rules">按专题浏览资料 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    {resourceCategories.map((cat) => (
      <div class="resource-section" id={cat.id}>
        <div class="topic-intro">
          <div class="resource-section-head">
            <div class="resource-section-icon">{cat.icon}</div>
            <div class="resource-section-head-text">
              <h2>{cat.name}<span class="resource-count">共 {cat.resources.length} 个资料包</span></h2>
              <p>{cat.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          {cat.learningPath && (
            <a class="guide-card" href={cat.learningPath.href}>
              <div class="guide-card-hint">推荐先读 · 学习路径</div>
              <h3>{cat.learningPath.title}</h3>
              <span class="guide-card-cta">看完整学习路径 →</span>
            </a>
          )}
        </div>

        <div class="resource-grid">
          {cat.resources.map((r) => (
            <article class="resource-card">
              <div class="resource-card-head">
                <div class="resource-card-tag">{cat.name}</div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="resource-card-title">{r.name}</h3>
              <div class="resource-card-meta">
                <div class="resource-card-meta-row">
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-label">适合谁用</span>
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-value">{r.audience}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-card-meta-row">
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-label">公开课场景</span>
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-value">{r.publicClassScene}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-card-meta-row">
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-label">实物内容</span>
                  <span class="resource-card-meta-value">{r.content}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="resource-card-actions">
                {detailPageSlugs[r.slug] ? (
                  <a class="resource-card-detail" href={`/resources/${detailPageSlugs[r.slug]}/`}>查看资料详情 →</a>
                ) : (
                  <a class="resource-card-detail" href={`/articles/${r.slug}/`}>查看文章 →</a>
                )}
                {detailPageSlugs[r.slug] && (
                  <a class="resource-card-article" href={`/articles/${r.slug}/`}>配套文章 →</a>
                )}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}

    <div class="conversion-note">
      <h2>使用资料包之前,先看这 3 条</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>资料包不是万能模板。</strong>
          同一份表格在不同产品、不同类目、不同时段填出来的结果,可能完全相反。资料包的价值是"让你知道该问什么问题",不是"替你做判断"。
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>需要结合产品、类目、广告阶段判断。</strong>
          新品期和成熟期用同一份 PPC 报表,看出来的结论会冲突。资料包里的字段是固定的,你的产品和阶段是动态的。
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>可以带到公开课或私域答疑中一起分析。</strong>
          公开课会基于真实学员的资料包填写数据,做现场拆解;私域答疑里可以贴自己的填写结果,带具体问题来。
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cases-helper">
      <div class="cases-helper-inner">
        <div class="cases-helper-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p>不知道资料怎么用？先看<span>实操案例</span>。</p>
